ea]]\n| 5\n| 1930\n|-\n| [[Juan Schiaffino]]\n| 5 (3\u20132)\n| 1950\u20131954\n|-\n| [[Carlos Borges]]\n| 4\n| 1954\n|-\n| [[Alcides Ghiggia]]\n| 4\n| 1950\n|-\n| [[Peregrino Anselmo]]\n| 3\n| 1930\n|-\n| [[Juan Hohberg]]\n| 3\n| 1954\n|}\n\n===Most games played in the World Cup===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Games\n! World Cups\n|-\n| '''[[Fernando Muslera]]'''\n| 16 (7\u20134\u20135)\n| 2010\u20132018\n|-\n| '''[[Edinson Cavani]]'''\n| 14 (6\u20134\u20134)\n| 2010\u20132018\n|-\n| '''[[Diego God\u00edn]]'''\n| 14 (5\u20134\u20135)\n| 2010\u20132018\n|-\n| [[Ladislao Mazurkiewicz]]\n| 13 (4\u20136\u20133)\n| 1966\u20131974\n|-\n| '''[[Luis Su\u00e1rez]]'''\n| 13 (6\u20132\u20135)\n| 2010\u20132018\n|-\n| [[Egidio Ar\u00e9valo R\u00edos]]\n| 11 (7\u20134)\n| 2010\u20132014\n|-\n| [[Julio C\u00e9sar Cort\u00e9s]]\n| 11 (1\u20134\u20136)\n| 1962\u20131970\n|-\n| '''[[Mart\u00edn C\u00e1ceres]]'''\n| 11 (2\u20134\u20135)\n| 2010\u20132018\n|-\n| [[Diego Forl\u00e1n]]\n| 10 (1\u20137\u20132)\n| 2002, 2010\u20132014\n|-\n| [[Maxi Pereira]]\n| 10 (7\u20133\u20130)\n| 2010\u20132018\n|-\n| [[Pedro Rocha]]\n| 10 (2\u20134\u20131\u20133)\n| 1962\u20131974\n|-\n| [[Luis Ubina]]\n| 10 (4\u20136)\n| 1966\u20131970\n|}\n\n===World Cup winning captains===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Name\n! Career\n! Caps\n! Goals\n|-\n| [[1930 FIFA World Cup|1930]]\n| [[Jos\u00e9 Nasazzi]]\n| 1923\u20131937\n| 41\n| 0\n|-\n| [[1950 FIFA World Cup|1950]]\n| [[Obdulio Varela]]\n| 1939\u20131954\n| 45\n| 9\n|}\n\n===Record against teams in the World Cup===\n{{updated|6 July 2018}} after the Quarter-finals match against France.    \n<!---THIS LIST IS ONLY FOR WORLD CUP MATCHES. DO NOT ADD STATISTICS FROM CONTINENTAL FINALS, FRIENDLIES, QUALIFIERS, OR OTHER MATCHES.!--->\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible collapsed\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 100%;\"\n|- style=\"color:black;\"\n!width=170|Opponents\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|Pld|Games played}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|W|Won}}